Instructions: Max Reps of: 5 Deadlifts ((85/60 kgs)), 5 Hang Power Cleans ((60/45 kgs)). Run 200m immediately after the 2 minutes.

Name: "5-Minute Max"
Instructions: Squat Cleans ((60/45 kgs)). 5 Minute Time Cap.

Name: "The Strict Complex"
Instructions: Odd: 3 Strict Pull-ups + 3 Strict Toes-to-Bar. Even: 3 Strict Dips + 3 Strict Press ((45/30 kgs)).

Name: "Triple Double-Under"
Instructions: Burpee Pull-ups (or Burpees), 3x Double Unders (i.e., 45-36-27).

Name: "Weighted Carry Repeater"
Instructions: 50 ft Farmer's Carry (Heavy), 50 ft Overhead Carry (Medium), 10 Push Press ((45/30 kgs)).

Name: "Bike/Run/Row Pyramid"
Instructions: Bike (Cals), Row (Cals), Ski (Cals). Complete one machine fully before moving to the next.

Name: "The Partner Clock"
Instructions: Partner A completes 10 Burpees. Partner B holds a Deadlift ((85/60 kgs)). Switch roles at the top of the next minute.

Name: "Strict Chipper"
Instructions: 25 Strict Pull-ups, 50 Strict Push-ups, 75 Strict Sit-ups, 100 Air Squats.

Name: "The Omega"
Instructions: 5 Rounds of: 10 Clean & Jerks ((70/50 kgs)), 20 Bar Muscle-Ups (or 30 C2B), 30 Alternating Pistol Squats. THEN: 1 Mile Run (with 20/14 lb Vest optional).
Training Goals: Maximal Strength Endurance, High-Skill Volume, Mental Toughness
